%% Diagram: Server-side data flow for grouped/sorted/filtered grid pages
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Grid as Grid (viewport)
    participant DS as ServerSide Datasource
    participant API as App API
    participant DB as Database / OLAP

    User->>Grid: scroll / sort / filter / expand group
    Grid->>DS: getRows({ startRow, endRow, sortModel, filterModel, groupKeys })
    DS->>API: POST /rows (request)
    API->>DB: SELECT … ORDER BY … WHERE … GROUP BY …
    DB-->>API: page slice + lastRow / aggregates
    API-->>DS: { rowData, rowCount }
    DS-->>Grid: success(rowData, rowCount)
    Grid-->>User: render block; update aria-rowcount / aria-rowindex

    Note over Grid,DB: Block cache keyed on (sortModel, filterModel, groupKeys)
